des:
Advanced Home app could control and scene your smart devices at home.
After connecting Alexa to your Advanced Home products in a few simple steps: 
1. Download our “Advanced Home” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “Advanced Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “Advanced Home” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
* Alexa, turn on kitchen light. 
* Alexa, turn off kitchen light. 
* Alexa, dim livingroom light.
* Alexa, brighten livingroom light. 
* Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent. 
* Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue.
